{"tid":1657151,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[真心] 係咪應該聲援一下加泰","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T10:04:45.000Z","uid":289809,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7da7240c386e4ffe2b8aecf408c2552f7c418119","tid":1657151,"uid":289809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>聲援加泰理據</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>對香港人</strong></span>: 幫大家回一回士氣, 香港人係抗爭路上有好多同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對加泰</span></strong>: 以下條Twitter 好sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;Isn't it horrible? Police beating peaceful protesters. Oh wait, this isn't Hong Kong, this is Catalonia, so no one cares.&quot; <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/moriyakari/status/1183862140089831424\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoriyakari%2Fstatus%2F1183862140089831424&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVoeNTHq1rgEicHo%2BkVhR8rs%3D&h=a79db965\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoriyakari%2Fstatus%2F1183862140089831424&h=fea6ba88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/moriyakari/status/1183862140089831424</a><br />\n<strong>的確, 香港人真係天之驕子, 舉手投足都好多人望住, 好多人support, 其他地方就無咁好彩。更加無咁有錢去抗爭。聲援下, 幫人打打氣, 同令世界多D關注</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">對世界</span></strong></span>: 由香港&quot;輸出&quot;抗爭同革命, 會大大力增加香港抗爭的矚目度, 同埋正當性。以後香港再做D咩, 會好自然比其他人傳, 同埋關心, 對我地百利無一害。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申, 小妹都係twitter 同FB 幫推加泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d4aca722cc8587c897f14c63b98dd3d36d3d38c","tid":1657151,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:04:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data